        <page n="04" image="pa.fr.fr.1864.05.18.04">
            <div type="a">
                <column>6</column>
                <head>Remember the Wounded</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <summary>The author exhorts the readership to remember the "twenty thousand of our
                    brave fathers, sons and brothers" who are "writhing under ghastly wounds in our
                    hospitals." He urges people to contribute money and supplies to the Christian
                    and Sanitary Commissions.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
            <pageNote>War news, continued from page one, fills most of this page.</pageNote>
        </page>
