        <page n="08" image="pa.fr.fr.1864.05.18.08">
            <div type="a">
                <column>2</column>
                <head>Town Cows--A Nuisance to be Abated</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>"Some thirty town cows are regularly turned loose by their owners every
                    morning to forage upon their neighbors, and they have become an intolerable
                    nuisance to all the citizens residing immediately around the town."</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <summary>People are warned to be responsible for their cows' grazing habits or else
                    risk having their animals seized by borough authorities and sold to owners who
                    will keep them off other people's property.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
